snippet.title: Wildgate | Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Introducing Wildgate—a new crew-based shooter featuring out-of-this-world spaceship combat and only three rules: outsmart, outrun, or outgun.

Sign up to playtest now: https://wildgate.gg/playtest 

Wishlist on Steam: https://wildgate.gg/steam 
Wishlist on PlayStation: https://wildgate.gg/playstation 
Wishlist on Xbox: https://wildgate.gg/xbox 

Visit our official website: https://playwildgate.com
Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/playwildgate 
Follow us on socials: https://linkt.ree/playwildgate
